 $\\ell_2$ norm/Lorentzian norm [21]. We first discuss how the\nvarious conditions required in our analysis can be verified, and then perform\nnumerical experiments to illustrate the convergence behaviors of SCP$_{ls}$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 20 Jan 2020 07:11:44 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 11 May 2021 12:56:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-05-12"}
