ak\nspectroscopic features of SNe Ic. High explosion energies combined with\nextensive mixing can produce red, broad-lined spectra, while minimal mixing and\na lower explosion energy produce bluer, narrow-lined spectra.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 20 Jan 2020 13:58:34 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 29 Jan 2020 13:26:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-02-05"}
